* * * * * * * * rat.c * * * * * * * *
* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *   
* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *   
A relative time frontend to at.

Invocation:
    rat HHMM
        executes supplied commands in HH hours, MM minutes
        Responds with ERR and returns 1 if my crappy time addition goes over
        2400

